, UNK, s'iz geven dort biz vifl yor: biz fuftsn yor, tsi vifl.

00:22:44.541 --> 00:22:47.491
iz gek- un ikh bin mitn,

00:22:47.491 --> 00:22:50.191
mit di shvester avekgegan in dem dorf

00:22:50.191 --> 00:22:51.150
haklen.

00:22:51.662 --> 00:22:57.562
mikh hot oysgelernt eyne fun Bukovine groyse shaln makhn, un keyner hot nisht gekent, nor ikh.

00:22:57.653 --> 00:22:59.683
fleg ikh zitsn dortn

00:22:59.683 --> 00:23:04.128
tsvey, dray vokhn, fun in der fri biz in der zinkediker nakht, haklen

00:23:04.128 --> 00:23:06.843
un makhn, un zi hot mir nokh batsolt markes...

00:23:06.850 --> 00:23:08.513
dentsmol ⟨gegan⟩ markes...

00:23:08.513 --> 00:23:12.179
un hot mir gegibn nokh a PODARKI, a broyt, mit dem.

00:23:12.179 --> 00:23:14.370
zenen mir gezesn in dorf.

00:23:14.747 --> 00:23:17.778
kumt tsu loyfn der bruder un zogt azoy:

00:23:17.802 --> 00:23:19.824
"m'iz gekumen in lager,

00:23:19.824 --> 00:23:26.812
un me farshraybt, un me nemt ale yesoymen keyn Rumenye, un fun dortn vet men otpraven keyn Erets-Yisroel, zogt men."

00:23:26.914 --> 00:23:31.119
un ikh her vi er ⟨SHUSH-⟩ mit zey, shtilerheyt zogt,

00:23:31.119 --> 00:23:35.872
"loz- lomir zi shikn. zi vet zikh tsun foter, efsher tsu der foter onrufn."

00:23:35.872 --> 00:23:37.963
az m- ikh hob nit gevust ver.

00:23:36.803 --> 00:23:42.821
dos iz geven beerekh in sof tsvey un fertsiker yor, tsi dray un fertsik⟨er⟩?

00:23:40.583 --> 00:23:45.214
azoy, azoy. di yorn gedenk ikh nit. azoy iz dos geven, tsvey un f-...

00:23:43.145 --> 00:23:43.694
neyn.

00:23:43.899 --> 00:23:45.928
in zumer efsher?

00:23:45.928 --> 00:23:47.141
s'iz shoyn geven...

00:23:45.983 --> 00:23:48.015
neyn, s'iz geven shoyn

00:23:48.015 --> 00:23:49.467
nokhn vinter,

00:23:49.467 --> 00:23:52.187
 nokh a mol eyn vinter.

00:23:49.496 --> 00:23:54.600
meglekh, meglekh dray un fertsiker yor, meglekh? yo.

00:23:52.513 --> 00:23:54.329
yo, yo.

00:23:54.538 --> 00:23:56.759
iz, zogt er azoy:

00:23:56.867 --> 00:23:59.595
"lomir..." az me zol mikh avekshikn.

00:24:00.276 --> 00:24:04.455
iz di eltere shvester, Basye, hot zikh genemen veynen.

00:24:04.815 --> 00:24:06.159
zogt zi, "neyn.

00:24:06.672 --> 00:24:10.693
undz ho'mir zi opgehit, un vos iz geven mit undz, tsi mir ho'mir zikh,

00:24:10.693 --> 00:24:15.528
⟨ho'm- ze'mir⟩ g-, ⟨zi⟩ iz geven mit undz, un itster shikn mir zi." un vos er zogt,

00:24:15.528 --> 00:24:18.666
"lomir zi shikn in der velt; zi vet uspeyen"...

00:24:18.666 --> 00:24:20.200
ir veyst s'heyst uspey⟨en⟩?

00:24:20.200 --> 00:24:24.915
"un, un efsher der foter vet zikh onrufn." ikh hob nit gevust voser a foter.

00:24:25.555 --> 00:24:27.574
un drum fregt men mikh.

00:24:27.597 --> 00:24:30.158
er iz gekumen mikh nemen, ikh zol shoyn forn.

00:24:30.158 --> 00:24:32.706
fregt men mikh, f- "nu, vi azoy zogstu?"

00:24:32.706 --> 00:24:33.749
zog ikh, "neyn."

00:24:34.330 --> 00:24:36.807
ikh vil nisht zey iberlozn:

00:24:36.807 --> 00:24:40.351
"aykh loz ikh nit iber, un for nisht in ergets." iker, ikh bin nisht geforn,

00:24:40.351 --> 00:24:43.996
nor eynike kinder vos zenen geforn, hobn baglikt,

00:24:43.996 --> 00:24:45.194
un eynike,

00:24:45.194 --> 00:24:49.978
⟨iz⟩, hot men dertronken, un s'iz geven groyse tragedyes.

00:24:49.978 --> 00:24:53.169
un ⟨e-⟩ un mayne, frayn⟨dn⟩,

00:24:53.169 --> 00:24:59.098
⟨,⟩ zey hobn zikh zeyer fil ongemutshet. m'hot zey farnemen azoy vi tsvey yesoymen, hobn, zey hobn keynem nisht gehat.

00:24:59.098 --> 00:25:01.460
itster zenen zey in Erets-Yisroel in kibuts.

00:25:01.460 --> 00:25:02.752
nor zey hobn dertseylt,

00:25:02.752 --> 00:25:05.502
shreklekh vos zey hobn mitgemakht un

00:25:05.502 --> 00:25:07.652
azoy zey zenen geblibn lebn.

00:25:07.945 --> 00:25:11.617
nu, bin ikh nisht geforn. ze'mir nokh geven dortn.

00:25:11.725 --> 00:25:16.338
azoy ho'mir zikh gedreyt un mir ho'mir ibergelebt. dos iz ⟨n-⟩....

00:25:16.551 --> 00:25:20.628
dortn ze'mir geven eyn mol in kolkhoz. s'iz ongekumen di daytshn,

00:25:20.685 --> 00:25:24.639
u⟨n⟩ ikh bin gezesn, ikh hob gearbet, un zi hot ergets geneyt.

00:25:24.639 --> 00:25:26.766
iz ongekumen atin daytshn,

00:25:26.766 --> 00:25:29.285
un az zey flegn kumen hobn zey shtark...

00:25:30.658 --> 00:25:34.513
un m'hot zikh genemen shlogn, un dort iz shoyn geven MESTN⟨e⟩ v-

00:25:34.513 --> 00:25:38.637
vos ⟨zey⟩ hobn zikh SOPRO⟨K⟩IVLYAYUT. hot men undz oyf a boydem gebahaltn.

00:25:38.637 --> 00:25:42.499
un a glik vos s'iz nisht geven keyn sakh daytshn. m'hot zikh geshlogn,

00:25:42.522 --> 00:25:46.054
un zey hobn gezogt az s'iz do do yidn, di yidn shlogn zikh.

00:25:46.054 --> 00:25:51.352
iker, m'hot zey oysgeharget, di etlekhe daytshn. undz ze'mir geblibn, dos iz geven oyf der nakht.

00:25:51.352 --> 00:25:52.939
far tog iz gekumen,

00:25:52.939 --> 00:25:59.073
 di tsvey shvester un veynen, "vos zol'mir tun? host gehert, azoy s'iz geven di nakht azoyns?

00:25:59.073 --> 00:26:02.481
azoy zol'mir aheymgeyn keyn Popovets, un vos zol'mir tun?"

00:26:02.481 --> 00:26:05.384
iker, undz veyn'mir un mir veys'mir nisht vos tsu tun.

00:26:05.384 --> 00:26:06.388
blaybn,

00:26:06.388 --> 00:26:09.957
iz dortn eynike, geven shtark laytishe mentshn

00:26:09.957 --> 00:26:13.054
tsvishn di Ukrayner. zenen geven gebidevete.

00:26:13.054 --> 00:26:16.789
zogt, ⟨h⟩ot, zogt er undz,

00:26:17.588 --> 00:26:20.434
"ikh zog aykh, heybt zikh oyf un geyt shoyn aheym,

00:26:20.625 --> 00:26:25.592
derfar vos, ir't blaybn ater, veln di daytshn azoy prost nisht lozn," az s'iz shoyn geven,

00:26:25.592 --> 00:26:27.583
m'hot zikh geshosn.

00:26:27.583 --> 00:26:29.157
"un geyt aheym,

00:26:29.316 --> 00:26:34.031
 keyn Popovets. anisht, zolt ir visn, morgn veln zey VSЁ RAVNO zayn do."

00:26:34.277 --> 00:26:35.776
iker, zog'mir,

00:26:35.776 --> 00:26:36.735
gey'mir.

00:26:36.876 --> 00:26:40.349
zeks a zeyger, fintster, UNK nokh nisht geven keyn zeks,

00:26:40.349 --> 00:26:42.793
ho'mir zikh ongetun, dray meydlekh.

00:26:42.951 --> 00:26:45.276
ze'mir aroysgegan nor funem dorf,

00:26:45.276 --> 00:26:49.576
ze'mir aroysgegan, un hot zikh gevalgert henitshkes daytshishe mit zakhn,

00:26:49.576 --> 00:26:52.370
mit alemen⟨s⟩. hobn mir gedarft dos ongetuekhts.

00:26:52.370 --> 00:26:53.745
mir ho'mir gornisht genemen.

00:26:53.852 --> 00:26:57.676
ze'mir gegangen durkhn vald. mir ho'mir shoyn arayn in vald arayn,

00:26:58.105 --> 00:27:00.506
ho'mir zikh shoyn gefreyt; ze'mir shoyn in vald.

00:27:00.506 --> 00:27:02.556
⟨undz⟩ ze'mir gegan tif in vald,

00:27:02.556 --> 00:27:05.307
un mir gey'mir nor aroys fun vald: fun oyvn,

00:27:05.307 --> 00:27:06.661
gib'mir a kuk,

00:27:06.661 --> 00:27:08.291
geyen beyde brider.

00:27:08.668 --> 00:27:13.370
zey hobn derhert az in ⟨Makikov⟩ iz azoyns forgekumen dort, m'hot zikh geshlogn,

00:27:13.370 --> 00:27:16.706
geyen zey zen vos s'iz mit undz geshen, tsi undz leb'mir tsi neyn.

00:27:16.706 --> 00:27:19.937
iz geven, zey hobn azoy geveynt un undz ho'mir geveynt.

00:27:19.937 --> 00:27:20.730
nor,

00:27:20.730 --> 00:27:25.030
s'iz shoyn geven, danken got, ze'mir shoyn geven in Popovets, do vu mir ho'mir gemegt.

00:27:25.105 --> 00:27:30.718
un, ⟨ah⟩, un dem andern tog, azoy undz ze'mir avekgegan, in der fri ongekumen fil daytshn in dorf.

00:27:30.724 --> 00:27:36.289
m'hot aroysgenemen vifl ire s'hobn gevoynt in dorf, hot men zey aroysgenemen droysn un m'hot zey oysgeshtelt.

00:27:36.289 --> 00:27:39.425
un m'hot gezogt, "git aroys di yidn vos zenen do gebahaltn.

00:27:40.107 --> 00:27:42.576
tomer nisht, hargen mir aykh ale oys."

00:27:42.576 --> 00:27:45.486
iz geven dort eyne a lererin oyf daytsh,

00:27:45.486 --> 00:27:47.250
vos zi hot gekent daytsh redn.

00:27:47.250 --> 00:27:53.395
iz zi aroysgegan un hot ongehoybn veynen un betn un dertseyln, az s'iz nishto do keyn yidn. zi veys nisht,

00:27:53.395 --> 00:27:56.351
ver s'hot gehat di ORUZHIE vos m'hot geshosn.

00:27:56.425 --> 00:28:00.261
un V OBSHCHEM, s'iz geven dort in dem dorf, azoy⟨ns ot o⟩.

00:28:00.261 --> 00:28:02.274
mir ho'mir eskapet mitn lebn.

00:28:02.432 --> 00:28:05.463
un drum ze'mir shoyn in Popovets alts geven.

00:28:05.892 --> 00:28:09.660
un drum iz ongekumen a prikaz

00:28:09.660 --> 00:28:14.418
az me zol tsunoyfnemen yungvarg, un me zol forn grobn koyln.

00:28:15.426 --> 00:28:20.297
iker, undz ze'mir geven ale yunge, ze'mir shoyn dort geven farshribn,

00:28:20.775 --> 00:28:24.658
iz, zogt er, me darf geyn grobn koyln.

00:28:24.658 --> 00:28:29.809
nu, undz ho'mir nisht gezogt neyn, vayl undz ho'mir moyre gehat; ⟨undz ho'mir⟩ dokh gevust az undz darf'mir do nisht zayn,

00:28:29.809 --> 00:28:31.181
un undz ze'mir do.

00:28:33.145 --> 00:28:34.084
nu,

00:28:34.123 --> 00:28:40.760
ho'mir zikh tsunoyfgenemen, un mir ze'mir geven in Popovets. fun dortn hot men undz geshikt keyn Kopaygorod,

00:28:40.760 --> 00:28:43.179
ongegruzet in di vagonen.

00:28:43.540 --> 00:28:47.140
froy Lipis, mir veln makhn itst a, a poyze,

00:28:47.140 --> 00:28:53.456
un ⟨ir ver-⟩ mir veln shpeter redn vegn dem, vos, vi ir hot gelebt in Popovets

00:28:53.597 --> 00:28:56.156
bay YUZI, dakht zikh mir,

00:28:56.466 --> 00:29:02.369
un ir vert dos ⟨d-⟩ vayter dertseyln. itst rut men zikh a bisl ⟨oyf⟩, nemt zikh a, epes oyf tsu trinken.

